<!-- Story -->
<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ai-summary">
      <strong>Summary:</strong> Osborne Electric & Contracting is a family-owned electrical contracting company based in Utah, founded by Trevor Osborne, a licensed Master Electrician. The company serves Salt Lake, Utah, Davis, Tooele, and Summit Counties with residential electrical services including panel upgrades, lighting installation, and emergency repairs. Every project is personally overseen with A+ workmanship standards.
    </div>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-image">
        <img src="/images/work/project-10.jpg" alt="Osborne Electric team at work on a Utah residential project" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Family-Owned, Customer-Focused</h2>
        <p>Osborne Electric & Contracting is a family-owned electrical contracting business founded by Trevor Osborne. As a licensed Master Electrician with years of experience, Trevor built this company on a simple principle: <strong>treat every job like it's your own home.</strong></p>
        <p>We've seen the problems that come from rushed work, cut corners, and electricians who don't care. That's not us. When we're in your home, we take the time to do things right because your safety and satisfaction matter to us.</p>
        <p>Whether it's a simple <a href="/services/residential-electrical/">outlet repair</a> or a complete <a href="/services/panel-upgrades/">panel upgrade</a>, we bring the same level of care and expertise to every project we take on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

